1. Test the AUP Banner (Computer policy)
    1. Restart the Windows 11 client VM
    2. Before you type a password, you should see the pop-up: "Security Warning: This system is for authorized use only"
    3. Success: Click OK

2. Test the Control Panel Lockout (User Policy)
    1. Log in as: jhr (The Restricted User)
    2. Once logged in, right-click the Start Button and try to open Settings or search for Control Panel
    3. Success: It should show a message: "This operation has been cancelled due to restrictions in effect on this computer."

3. Test the Admin (Control Check)
    1. Sign out of jhr
    2. Sign in as jadmin
    3. Try to open Settings/Control Panel
    4. Success: It opens normally (because the policy was only applied to the General_Staff OU, not the Admin_Staff OU)
